<br>
When ER has had raid conflicts in Fear, the IGB guilds have been very accomadating on the epic drops, so this isn't a dispute I myself have had. Hell ML helped us greatly with the Epic guy who was up on our conflict. They pulled it, we killed it. They were awesome, and their cooperation is appreciated. Do I think everyone SHOULD go to that extent? NO. But, if the non IGB guild can take the Golems and Epics alone, then they reserved it for that reason, they should get them.<br>
<br>
 It doesn't seem that CT or even Fear is the dispute but the Golems and epics are. If IGB wants to do Fear for the epic guys, then post it here. It seems simple and its all about cooperation and respect.<br>
<br>
It seems easy to say, well the little guild should just go the next night, this isn't always possible with a small guild with a smaller base membership. If everyone has to show to make it possible, people have lives. <br>
<br>
I have no conflict with uber guilds, it is just a different EQ lifestyle and has its own rewards and its own drawbacks. Same as a smaller guild. Understanding is needed. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub16.ezboard.com/fdruzzilro86846generaldiscussion.showMessage?topicID=1748.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub16.ezboard.com/fdruzzilro86846generaldiscussion.showMessage?topicID=1747.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub16.ezboard.com/fdruzzilro86846generaldiscussion.emailToFriend?topicID=1729.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub16.ezboard.com/fdruzzilro86846generaldiscussion.threadControl?topicID=1729.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub16.ezboard.com/fdruzzilro86846generaldiscussion.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1729.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub16.ezboard.com/fdruzzilro86846generaldiscussion.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1729.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub16.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="druzzilro86846generaldiscussion">General Discussion<option value="druzzilro86846frm10">IRL<option value="druzzilro86846frm8">Raids<option value="druzzilro86846marketplace">Market Place<option value="druzzilro86846questsinfoandhelp"